org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.providers

Interface OWLVocabularyProvider

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DatatypeExpressionProvider, OWLDataFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OWLDataFactoryImpl

    public interface OWLVocabularyProvider
    Utility shortcuts for OWL basic entities. For the sake of convenience, this also includes RDF/RDFS and XSD entities.
